            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間12日09:31，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲131.13點（或3%），暫報4505.20點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-5%</li><li>近 1 月：-13.9%</li><li>近 3 月：-13%</li><li>近 6 月：-10.92%</li><li>今年以來：-12.17%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)領漲。英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)上漲5.28%；輝達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>)上漲5.28%；邁威爾科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRVL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRVL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRVL-US</a>)上漲4.94%；美光科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>)上漲4.93%；連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CO